Key Match Events: Aaron Civale pitched seven shutout innings and allowed only four baserunners
Jackson Chourio doubled in a pair of runs in the fourth inning
William Contreras scored on a steal of home in the third inning
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Brewers improved to 77-56 with a 6-0 victory over the San Francisco Giants
Aaron Civale improved to 5-8 and lowered his season ERA to 4.59
Jackson Chourio drove in runs in six of his last eight games and has 62 RBIs in 120 games
